@page "/me/llm-wiki"
@inject SlogsAuthState AuthState
@inject SlogsApiClient ApiClient
@inject NavigationManager Navigation
@inject IJSRuntime JS

<PageTitle>LLM Wiki</PageTitle>
<SeoHead Title="LLM Wiki | slogs" Description="개인 LLM Wiki를 검색하고 읽습니다." NoIndex="true" />

@if (CurrentUser is null)
{
    <p class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 text-slate-500">로그인이 필요합니다. <a class="font-semibold underline" href="@GetLoginHref()">로그인</a>해 주세요.</p>
}
else
{
    <section class="space-y-5">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-3 border-b border-slate-200 pb-4">
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">LLM Wiki</h1>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">@CurrentUser.DisplayName 님의 LLM Wiki입니다.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section id="usage" class="scroll-mt-24 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 lg:flex-row lg:items-start lg:justify-between">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-slate-500">동작 원리</p>
                    <h2 class="mt-1 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">LLM Wiki는 기록을 GraphRAG 기억으로 바꿉니다</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="max-w-2xl text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
                    자연어로 남긴 기록은 제목, 태그, 프롬프트, 본문을 함께 인덱싱합니다. 검색할 때는 서버 로컬 EmbeddingGemma와 PostgreSQL pgvector, graph node 관계 점수를 결합해 관련 기억을 찾고 관련도 퍼센트를 표시합니다.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-5 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">1. 기록</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">사용자가 남긴 결정, 선호, 판단 기준, 프로젝트 맥락을 하나의 Wiki 항목으로 저장합니다. 제목과 태그도 검색 신호로 함께 쓰입니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">2. 의미와 관계 인덱싱</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">내용은 768차원 embedding으로 저장되고, 제목 phrase, 태그, 핵심어는 graph node로 저장됩니다. 한국어 조사 차이는 graph token 정규화로 줄입니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">3. 관련도 검색</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">검색어 embedding과 graph node를 함께 비교해 순위를 만들고, 낮은 관련도 결과는 제외합니다. 퍼센트는 통계적 확률이 아니라 GraphRAG 관련도 점수입니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-5 grid gap-5 border-t border-slate-200 pt-5 lg:grid-cols-2">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">LLM Agent 정책에 반영할 핵심</h3>
                    <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1.5 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
                        <li>이전 결정, 선호, 판단 기준, 프로젝트 맥락이 관련되면 Slogs LLM Wiki를 먼저 조회합니다.</li>
                        <li><code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1 py-0.5 text-xs text-slate-800">search</code>는 후보 요약 목록, <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1 py-0.5 text-xs text-slate-800">recall</code>은 답변/구현에 바로 적용할 압축 컨텍스트로 구분합니다.</li>
                        <li>MCP 응답의 Retrieval Diagnostics로 결과 수, limit, categoryPath, minRelevancePercent, elapsedMs를 확인해 검색 품질을 평가합니다.</li>
                        <li>작업을 마치기 전, 장기적으로 문서화나 자동화에 도움이 될 암묵지 저장 후보를 조용히 점검합니다.</li>
                        <li>저장 전에는 관련 기억을 먼저 찾고, 중복이면 새 항목이 아니라 기존 항목을 merge/update합니다.</li>
                        <li>정제된 현재 기억과 별도로 원래 저장/병합/갱신 요청은 Raw Provenance에 남겨 검색 품질과 병합 품질을 검증합니다.</li>
                        <li>저장, 병합, 갱신 시 프로젝트/영역/주제를 나타내는 <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1 py-0.5 text-xs text-slate-800">categoryPath</code>를 명시합니다.</li>
                        <li>복사한 프롬프트는 Slogs MCP 키 입력과 전역/프로젝트/현재 세션 범위 선택을 안내하고, 선택한 범위에 맞춰 MCP 연결도 함께 설정하도록 합니다.</li>
                        <li>한국어 <a class="font-semibold text-slate-900 underline" href="/prompts/slogs-mcp.ko.md" target="_blank">slogs-mcp.ko.md</a>와 English <a class="font-semibold text-slate-900 underline" href="/prompts/slogs-mcp.en.md" target="_blank">slogs-mcp.en.md</a>를 언어별 프롬프트로 제공합니다.</li>
                        <li>동기화는 버전 URL <a class="font-semibold text-slate-900 underline" href="/prompts/slogs-mcp.version" target="_blank">slogs-mcp.version</a>을 먼저 비교하고, 버전이 같으면 프롬프트 다운로드, 키 요청, 범위 선택을 반복하지 않습니다.</li>
                        <li>API 키, 비밀번호, 토큰, 일회성 로그, 임시 실행 내역은 저장하지 않습니다.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">Agent 동작 흐름</h3>
                    <ol class="mt-2 list-decimal space-y-1.5 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
                        <li>사용자 요청이 이전 맥락과 관련되는지 판단합니다.</li>
                        <li>넓거나 애매한 요청은 먼저 <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1 py-0.5 text-xs text-slate-800">search</code>로 작은 후보 목록을 확인합니다.</li>
                        <li>답변이나 구현에 바로 적용할 맥락은 낮은 limit의 <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1 py-0.5 text-xs text-slate-800">recall</code>로 불러옵니다.</li>
                        <li>관련도, 제목, 요약, 태그, Retrieval Diagnostics를 보고 현재 작업에 필요한 기억을 선별합니다.</li>
                        <li>상위 결과가 엉뚱하거나 느리거나 너무 크면 query, categoryPath, limit, minRelevancePercent를 좁혀 다시 조회합니다.</li>
                        <li>새 기억이 필요하면 <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1 py-0.5 text-xs text-slate-800">capture/find_related</code> 후 <code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1 py-0.5 text-xs text-slate-800">categoryPath</code>를 정하고 저장합니다.</li>
                        <li>항목을 열어 Raw Provenance의 원문 근거와 현재 통합 기억이 일치하는지 점검합니다.</li>
                        <li>일회성 로그, 임시 실행 내역, 검증되지 않은 추측, 현재 파일에서 쉽게 복구 가능한 단순 사실은 저장하지 않습니다.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-5 border-t border-slate-200 pt-5">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 lg:flex-row lg:items-start lg:justify-between">
                    <div class="max-w-2xl">
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-slate-500">Agent Prompt</p>
                        <h3 class="mt-1 text-base font-bold text-slate-900">언어별 완성 프롬프트</h3>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
                            복사되는 프롬프트는 선택한 언어 하나만 포함합니다. 처음 설치할 때만 Agent가 Slogs MCP 키를 요청하고 전역, 현재 프로젝트, 현재 세션 중 적용 범위를 묻도록 안내합니다.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs font-semibold">
                        <a class="rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-50"
                           href="@SlogsMcpPolicyPrompt.VersionPath"
                           target="_blank">버전 URL</a>
                        <a class="rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-50"
                           href="@SlogsMcpPolicyPrompt.KoreanPublicPath"
                           target="_blank">한국어 URL</a>
                        <a class="rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-50"
                           href="@SlogsMcpPolicyPrompt.EnglishPublicPath"
                           target="_blank">English URL</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-4 grid gap-3 lg:grid-cols-2">
                    <div class="@GetKoreanPromptCardClass()">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">한국어 프롬프트</p>
                            <p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-slate-500">한국어 지침만 포함합니다. 최초 설치 시 MCP 키와 적용 범위를 묻도록 안내합니다.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <button class="rounded-full border border-slate-300 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-100"
                                    type="button"
                                    @onclick="SelectKoreanPrompt">
                                미리보기
                            </button>
                            <button class="rounded-full bg-slate-900 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-slate-800"
                                    type="button"
                                    @onclick="CopyKoreanAgentPromptAsync">
                                한국어 복사
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="@GetEnglishPromptCardClass()">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">English Prompt</p>
                            <p class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-slate-500">English instructions only. It asks for the MCP key and scope only during initial installation.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <button class="rounded-full border border-slate-300 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-100"
                                    type="button"
                                    @onclick="SelectEnglishPrompt">
                                Preview
                            </button>
                            <button class="rounded-full bg-slate-900 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-slate-800"
                                    type="button"
                                    @onclick="CopyEnglishAgentPromptAsync">
                                Copy English
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-4 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-slate-950 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-b border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-slate-600">Preview</p>
                            <h4 class="mt-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-950">@GetSelectedPromptTitle()</h4>
                            <p class="mt-1 break-all text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700">@GetSelectedPromptUrl()</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                            @if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(copyPromptMessage))
                            {
                                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-700">@copyPromptMessage</span>
                            }
                            <button class="rounded-full bg-slate-900 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-slate-800"
                                    type="button"
                                    @onclick="CopySelectedAgentPromptAsync">
                                선택한 프롬프트 복사
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <pre class="max-h-96 overflow-auto whitespace-pre-wrap break-words p-4 text-xs leading-5 text-slate-100"><code>@GetSelectedAgentPrompt()</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="search" class="scroll-mt-24 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">검색</h2>
                <div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 gap-2 md:max-w-lg">
                    <input class="min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-sm outline-none focus:border-slate-500"
                           placeholder="검색어"
                           @bind="searchQuery"
                           @bind:event="oninput"
                           @onkeydown="HandleSearchKeyDown" />
                    <button class="rounded-xl bg-slate-900 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-slate-800 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-60"
                            type="button"
                            disabled="@isSearching"
                            @onclick="SearchEntriesAsync">
                        @(isSearching ? "검색 중..." : "검색")
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-3" data-llm-wiki-category-panel="true">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">카테고리</p>
                        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">카테고리로 좁힌 뒤 아래 카드 그리드에서 Wiki를 선택합니다.</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="w-fit rounded-full bg-white px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">@($"{categories.Count}개")</span>
                </div>
                @if (categories.Count == 0)
                {
                    <p class="mt-3 rounded-lg border border-dashed border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-4 text-center text-sm text-slate-500">카테고리가 없습니다.</p>
                }
                else
                {
                    <div class="mt-3 grid max-h-64 gap-2 overflow-y-auto pr-1 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 2xl:grid-cols-4">
                        <button class="@GetCategoryButtonClass(null)"
                                type="button"
                                @onclick="() => SelectCategoryAsync(null)">
                            <span class="min-w-0">
                                <span class="block truncate">전체</span>
                                <span class="mt-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400">모든 카테고리</span>
                            </span>
                            <span class="shrink-0 rounded-full bg-white px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">@GetTotalCategoryCount()</span>
                        </button>
                        @foreach (var category in categories)
                        {
                            var categoryHint = GetCategoryHint(category.CategoryPath);
                            <button class="@GetCategoryButtonClass(category.CategoryPath)"
                                    type="button"
                                    title="@categoryHint"
                                    aria-label="@categoryHint"
                                    @onclick="() => SelectCategoryAsync(category.CategoryPath)">
                                <span class="min-w-0 space-y-0.5 cursor-help"
                                      title="@categoryHint"
                                      data-llm-wiki-category-path="true">
                                    @foreach (var segment in GetCategorySegments(category.CategoryPath))
                                    {
                                        <span class="block truncate"
                                              title="@categoryHint"
                                              data-llm-wiki-category-segment="true">@segment</span>
                                    }
                                    <span class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400">@($"깊이 {category.CategoryDepth}")</span>
                                </span>
                                <span class="shrink-0 rounded-full bg-white px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">@category.Count</span>
                            </button>
                        }
                    </div>
                }
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4">
                <section class="space-y-3" data-llm-wiki-results="true">
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">@GetCategoryBreadcrumb(activeCategoryPath ?? string.Empty)</p>
                            <h3 class="mt-1 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Wiki 카드</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">@($"{results.Count}개 표시 중")</p>
                    </div>

                    @if (results.Count == 0)
                    {
                        <p class="rounded-xl border border-dashed border-slate-300 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-6 text-center text-sm text-slate-500">@GetEmptyMessage()</p>
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        <div class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 2xl:grid-cols-4">
                            @foreach (var result in results)
                            {
                                var resultCategoryHint = GetCategoryHint(result.CategoryPath);
                                <button class="@GetResultButtonClass(result)"
                                        data-llm-wiki-card="true"
                                        type="button"
                                        @onclick="() => SelectEntryAsync(result)">
                                    <span class="mb-3 flex items-start justify-between gap-2">
                                        <span class="min-w-0 cursor-help rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-bold leading-4 text-slate-600"
                                              title="@resultCategoryHint"
                                              data-llm-wiki-card-category-path="true">
                                            @foreach (var segment in GetCategorySegments(result.CategoryPath))
                                            {
                                                <span class="block truncate"
                                                      title="@resultCategoryHint"
                                                      data-llm-wiki-category-segment="true">@segment</span>
                                            }
                                        </span>
                                        <span class="shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap rounded-full bg-slate-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400">@($"깊이 {result.CategoryDepth}")</span>
                                    </span>
                                    <span class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2">
                                        <span class="min-w-0 break-words text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">@result.Title</span>
                                        @if (result.RelevancePercent is not null)
                                        {
                                            <span class="shrink-0 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-emerald-800">@($"{result.RelevancePercent}%")</span>
                                        }
                                    </span>
                                    @if (result.RelevancePercent is not null)
                                    {
                                        <span class="mt-2 block h-1.5 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-slate-100">
                                            <span class="block h-full rounded-full bg-emerald-500" style="@GetRelevanceBarStyle(result.RelevancePercent.Value)"></span>
                                        </span>
                                    }
                                    <span class="mt-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-500">
                                        <span>@FormatDateTime(result.UpdatedAt)</span>
                                        <span>@($"{result.AccessCount}회 열람")</span>
                                    </span>
                                    @if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(result.Summary))
                                    {
                                        <span class="mt-2 block text-sm leading-5 text-slate-700">@Shorten(result.Summary, 160)</span>
                                    }
                                    @if (result.Tags.Count > 0)
                                    {
                                        <span class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-1">
                                            @foreach (var tag in result.Tags)
                                            {
                                                <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-sky-900">#@tag</span>
                                            }
                                        </span>
                                    }
                                </button>
                            }
                        </div>

                        <InfiniteScrollSentinel Visible="@(results.Count > 0)"
                                                HasMore="@hasMoreResults"
                                                IsLoading="@isLoadingMore"
                                                OnLoadMore="LoadMoreEntriesAsync"
                                                LoadingText="다음 Wiki를 불러오는 중..."
                                                DoneText="더 이상 표시할 Wiki가 없습니다."
                                                ShowDoneText="@(!hasMoreResults && !isLoading && !isSearching)" />
                    }
                </section>
            </div>
        </section>
    </section>

    @if (selectedEntry is not null)
    {
        <div class="fixed inset-0 z-50 grid place-items-center overflow-y-auto bg-slate-950/40 p-4 backdrop-blur-sm"
             style="z-index: 1000;"
             data-llm-wiki-detail-modal="true"
             role="presentation"
             @onclick="CloseSelectedEntry">
            <article class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-4xl flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-2xl"
                     style="max-height: calc(100vh - 2rem);"
                     role="dialog"
                     aria-modal="true"
                     aria-labelledby="llm-wiki-detail-title"
                     @onclick:stopPropagation="true">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-slate-200 px-5 py-4">
                    <div class="min-w-0">
                        <p class="mb-2 inline-flex max-w-full cursor-help items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-slate-50 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-bold text-slate-600"
                           title="@GetCategoryHint(selectedEntry.CategoryPath)">
                            <span class="min-w-0 truncate">@GetCategoryBreadcrumb(selectedEntry.CategoryPath)</span>
                            <span class="shrink-0 text-slate-400">@($"깊이 {selectedEntry.CategoryDepth}")</span>
                        </p>
                        <h3 id="llm-wiki-detail-title" class="break-words text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">@selectedEntry.Title</h3>
                        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">@FormatDateTime(selectedEntry.UpdatedAt)</p>
                    </div>
                    <button class="shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 transition hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50"
                            type="button"
                            @onclick="CloseSelectedEntry">
                        닫기
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-4 overflow-y-auto px-5 py-4">
                    @if (selectedEntry.Tags.Count > 0)
                    {
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
                            @foreach (var tag in selectedEntry.Tags)
                            {
                                <span class="rounded-full bg-sky-50 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-sky-900">#@tag</span>
                            }
                        </div>
                    }
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-slate-500">Prompt</p>
                        <pre class="mt-1 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words rounded-lg bg-slate-50 p-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-800">@selectedEntry.SourcePrompt</pre>
                    </div>
                    @if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(selectedEntry.Content))
                    {
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-slate-500">Content</p>
                            <pre class="mt-1 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words rounded-lg bg-slate-50 p-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-800">@selectedEntry.Content</pre>
                        </div>
                    }
                    @if (selectedEntry.Sources.Count > 0)
                    {
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-slate-500">Raw Provenance</p>
                            <div class="mt-1 grid gap-2">
                                @foreach (var source in selectedEntry.Sources.OrderBy(x => x.CreatedAt))
                                {
                                    <details class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-3">
                                        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">
                                            <span>@source.Action</span>
                                            <span class="ml-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">@FormatDateTime(source.CreatedAt)</span>
                                        </summary>
                                        <div class="mt-3 grid gap-3">
                                            @if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(source.Title)
                                                || !string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(source.Tags)
                                                || !string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(source.CategoryPath))
                                            {
                                                <div class="grid gap-1 text-xs text-slate-600">
                                                    @if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(source.Title))
                                                    {
                                                        <p><span class="font-bold text-slate-800">title</span> @source.Title</p>
                                                    }
                                                    @if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(source.Tags))
                                                    {
                                                        <p><span class="font-bold text-slate-800">tags</span> @source.Tags</p>
                                                    }
                                                    @if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(source.CategoryPath))
                                                    {
                                                        <p><span class="font-bold text-slate-800">categoryPath</span> @source.CategoryPath</p>
                                                    }
                                                </div>
                                            }
                                            <div>
                                                <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-slate-500">Raw Prompt</p>
                                                <pre class="mt-1 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words rounded-lg bg-white p-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-800">@source.Prompt</pre>
                                            </div>
                                            @if (source.Content is not null)
                                            {
                                                <div>
                                                    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase text-slate-500">Raw Content</p>
                                                    <pre class="mt-1 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words rounded-lg bg-white p-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-800">@source.Content</pre>
                                                </div>
                                            }
                                        </div>
                                    </details>
                                }
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    }
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
    }
}

@code {
    private const int PageSize = 20;
    private const int MinSearchRelevancePercent = 50;
    private const string KoreanPromptLanguage = "ko";
    private const string EnglishPromptLanguage = "en";

    private AuthUser? CurrentUser => AuthState.CurrentUser;
    private List<LlmWikiSearchResult> results = [];
    private IReadOnlyList<LlmWikiCategorySummary> categories = [];
    private LlmWikiEntryResponse? selectedEntry;
    private string searchQuery = string.Empty;
    private string activeSearchQuery = string.Empty;
    private string? activeCategoryPath;
    private string selectedPromptLanguage = KoreanPromptLanguage;
    private string copyPromptMessage = string.Empty;
    private bool isLoading;
    private bool isSearching;
    private bool isLoadingMore;
    private bool hasMoreResults;

    protected override async Task OnInitializedAsync()
    {
        await AuthState.EnsureInitializedAsync();
        if (CurrentUser is null)
        {
            Navigation.NavigateTo(GetLoginHref());
            return;
        }

        await LoadAsync();
    }

    private async Task LoadAsync()
    {
        if (CurrentUser is null || isLoading)
        {
            return;
        }

        isLoading = true;
        try
        {
            categories = await ApiClient.GetLlmWikiCategoriesAsync(CurrentUser.UserName);
            activeSearchQuery = NormalizeSearchQuery(searchQuery);
            await LoadEntriesPageAsync(reset: true);
        }
        finally
        {
            isLoading = false;
        }
    }

    private async Task SearchEntriesAsync()
    {
        if (CurrentUser is null || isSearching)
        {
            return;
        }

        isSearching = true;
        try
        {
            activeSearchQuery = NormalizeSearchQuery(searchQuery);
            await LoadEntriesPageAsync(reset: true);
        }
        finally
        {
            isSearching = false;
        }
    }

    private async Task LoadMoreEntriesAsync()
    {
        if (CurrentUser is null || isLoading || isSearching || isLoadingMore || !hasMoreResults)
        {
            return;
        }

        isLoadingMore = true;
        try
        {
            await LoadEntriesPageAsync(reset: false);
        }
        finally
        {
            isLoadingMore = false;
        }
    }

    private async Task LoadEntriesPageAsync(bool reset)
    {
        if (CurrentUser is null)
        {
            return;
        }

        if (reset)
        {
            results = [];
            selectedEntry = null;
            hasMoreResults = false;
        }

        var batch = await ApiClient.SearchLlmWikiAsync(
            CurrentUser.UserName,
            activeSearchQuery,
            PageSize,
            results.Count,
            MinSearchRelevancePercent,
            activeCategoryPath);
        var knownIds = results.Select(x => x.Id).ToHashSet();
        results.AddRange(batch.Where(x => !knownIds.Contains(x.Id)));
        hasMoreResults = batch.Count == PageSize;
    }

    private async Task SelectCategoryAsync(string? categoryPath)
    {
        if (CurrentUser is null || isLoading || isSearching || isLoadingMore)
        {
            return;
        }

        activeCategoryPath = string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(categoryPath) ? null : categoryPath;
        activeSearchQuery = NormalizeSearchQuery(searchQuery);
        isSearching = true;
        try
        {
            await LoadEntriesPageAsync(reset: true);
        }
        finally
        {
            isSearching = false;
        }
    }

    private async Task SelectEntryAsync(LlmWikiSearchResult result)
    {
        if (CurrentUser is null)
        {
            return;
        }

        selectedEntry = await ApiClient.GetLlmWikiEntryAsync(CurrentUser.UserName, result.Id.ToString());
    }

    private void CloseSelectedEntry()
        => selectedEntry = null;

    private void SelectKoreanPrompt()
    {
        selectedPromptLanguage = KoreanPromptLanguage;
        copyPromptMessage = string.Empty;
    }

    private void SelectEnglishPrompt()
    {
        selectedPromptLanguage = EnglishPromptLanguage;
        copyPromptMessage = string.Empty;
    }

    private async Task CopySelectedAgentPromptAsync()
        => await CopyPromptTextAsync(GetSelectedAgentPrompt(), GetSelectedCopyMessage());

    private async Task CopyKoreanAgentPromptAsync()
    {
        selectedPromptLanguage = KoreanPromptLanguage;
        await CopyPromptTextAsync(SlogsMcpPolicyPrompt.BuildKoreanMarkdown(), "한국어 프롬프트가 복사되었습니다.");
    }

    private async Task CopyEnglishAgentPromptAsync()
    {
        selectedPromptLanguage = EnglishPromptLanguage;
        await CopyPromptTextAsync(SlogsMcpPolicyPrompt.BuildEnglishMarkdown(), "English prompt copied.");
    }

    private string GetSelectedAgentPrompt()
        => selectedPromptLanguage == EnglishPromptLanguage
            ? SlogsMcpPolicyPrompt.BuildEnglishMarkdown()
            : SlogsMcpPolicyPrompt.BuildKoreanMarkdown();

    private string GetSelectedPromptTitle()
        => selectedPromptLanguage == EnglishPromptLanguage
            ? "English Prompt"
            : "한국어 프롬프트";

    private string GetSelectedPromptUrl()
        => selectedPromptLanguage == EnglishPromptLanguage
            ? SlogsMcpPolicyPrompt.DefaultEnglishPublicUrl
            : SlogsMcpPolicyPrompt.DefaultKoreanPublicUrl;

    private string GetSelectedCopyMessage()
        => selectedPromptLanguage == EnglishPromptLanguage
            ? "English prompt copied."
            : "한국어 프롬프트가 복사되었습니다.";

    private string GetKoreanPromptCardClass()
        => GetPromptCardClass(KoreanPromptLanguage);

    private string GetEnglishPromptCardClass()
        => GetPromptCardClass(EnglishPromptLanguage);

    private string GetPromptCardClass(string language)
    {
        var isSelected = string.Equals(selectedPromptLanguage, language, StringComparison.Ordinal);
        return isSelected
            ? "rounded-xl border border-slate-900 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm ring-2 ring-slate-900/10"
            : "rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm transition hover:border-slate-300";
    }

    private async Task CopyPromptTextAsync(string text, string message)
    {
        await JS.InvokeVoidAsync("navigator.clipboard.writeText", text);
        copyPromptMessage = message;
    }

    private async Task HandleSearchKeyDown(KeyboardEventArgs e)
    {
        if (e.Key == "Enter")
        {
            await SearchEntriesAsync();
        }
    }

    private string GetLoginHref()
    {
        var uri = new Uri(Navigation.Uri);
        var safeReturn = string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(uri.Query) ? uri.AbsolutePath : uri.PathAndQuery;
        return $"/login?returnUrl={Uri.EscapeDataString(safeReturn)}";
    }

    private static string FormatDateTime(DateTime dateTime)
        => dateTime.ToLocalTime().ToString("yyyy.MM.dd HH:mm");

    private string GetEmptyMessage()
    {
        if (isLoading || isSearching)
        {
            return "검색 중입니다.";
        }

        if (!string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(activeCategoryPath) && string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(activeSearchQuery))
        {
            return "선택한 카테고리에 표시할 LLM Wiki가 없습니다.";
        }

        return string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(activeSearchQuery)
            ? "저장된 LLM Wiki가 없습니다."
            : "검색 결과가 없습니다.";
    }

    private string GetResultButtonClass(LlmWikiSearchResult result)
    {
        var selected = selectedEntry?.Id == result.Id;
        return selected
            ? "block h-full w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-900 bg-white px-4 py-4 text-left shadow-sm ring-2 ring-slate-900/10 transition"
            : "block h-full w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-4 text-left shadow-sm transition hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50 hover:shadow";
    }

    private string GetCategoryButtonClass(string? categoryPath)
    {
        var isActive = string.Equals(activeCategoryPath ?? string.Empty, categoryPath ?? string.Empty, StringComparison.Ordinal);
        return isActive
            ? "flex min-h-24 w-full items-start justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-900 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-left text-sm font-bold text-slate-900"
            : "flex min-h-24 w-full items-start justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-transparent bg-white/60 px-3 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 transition hover:border-slate-200 hover:bg-white";
    }

    private int GetTotalCategoryCount()
        => categories.Where(x => x.CategoryDepth == 1).Sum(x => x.Count);

    private static string GetCategoryBreadcrumb(string categoryPath)
        => string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(categoryPath)
            ? "general"
            : categoryPath.Replace("/", " / ", StringComparison.Ordinal);

    private static string GetCategoryHint(string categoryPath)
        => GetCategoryBreadcrumb(categoryPath);

    private static IReadOnlyList<string> GetCategorySegments(string categoryPath)
    {
        if (string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(categoryPath))
        {
            return ["general"];
        }

        var segments = categoryPath.Split('/', StringSplitOptions.RemoveEmptyEntries | StringSplitOptions.TrimEntries);
        return segments.Length == 0 ? ["general"] : segments;
    }

    private static string GetRelevanceBarStyle(int relevancePercent)
        => $"width: {Math.Clamp(relevancePercent, 0, 100)}%;";

    private static string NormalizeSearchQuery(string value)
        => value.Trim();

    private static string Shorten(string text, int maxLength)
    {
        if (string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(text))
        {
            return string.Empty;
        }

        return text.Length <= maxLength ? text : text[..maxLength] + "...";
    }
}
